[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Input Methods:**                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - URL Parameter: `name` (GET request to `/page?name=...`)                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The parameter is reflected into an HTML input field's `value` attribute    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Authentication:**                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No authentication required - public endpoint accessible without            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m credentials                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **XSS Injection Point:**                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The `/page` endpoint accepts a `name` parameter that is reflected directly   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m into the HTML response inside an input field's `value` attribute:            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <input type=text name=name placeholder="Enter your name..." value="[USER     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m INPUT]">                                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Exploitation:**                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The input relies on attribute value escaping (`value="..."`), but double     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m quotes can be injected to break out of the attribute context and inject      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m event handlers directly into the input element.                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
