[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Effect Analysis:**                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The reflective XSS executes `alert('XSS')` when the input field receives   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m focus                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The page indicates success (image changed from `error_circle.png` to       [32m│[0m
